tool_description: This API lets you check whether a domain is available for registration or not. Please report false positives.
name: Domain Availability Checker
title: Domain Availability Checker

api_list.name: NAME TLD
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://domainstatus.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "domainstatus.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
